INSERT INTO `article` VALUES (14, '配置HTTPS的方法（nginx的）', '配置HTTPS的方法nginx版  , apache的并不适用', '<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; ssl_certificate&nbsp; &nbsp; /etc/letsencrypt/live/chengguan.com/fullchain.pem;</p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; ssl_certificate_key&nbsp; &nbsp; /etc/letsencrypt/live/chengguan.com/privkey.pem;</p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; ssl_protocols TLSv1 TLSv1.1 TLSv1.2;</p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; ssl_ciphers ECDHE-RSA-AES128-GCM-SHA256:HIGH:!aNULL:!MD5:!RC4:!DHE;</p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; ssl_prefer_server_ciphers on;</p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; ssl_session_cache shared:SSL:10m;</p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; ssl_session_timeout 10m;</p><p><br/></p><p><br/></p><p><br/></p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; ssl_certificate&nbsp; &nbsp; /etc/letsencrypt/live/chengguan.com/fullchain.pem;</p><p>放&nbsp; .pem文件</p><p><br/></p><p>&nbsp;ssl_certificate_key&nbsp; &nbsp; /etc/letsencrypt/live/chengguan.com/privkey.pem;</p><p>放 .key文件</p><p><br/></p><p>记得重启nginx</p>', '2020-04-03 15:19:55', 2, NULL, NULL, '2020-04-03 15:24:02');

